{"word":"προοράω","slug":"προοράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προοράω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁράω\">ὁράω</a></el>] ‘see what is ahead’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in spatial sense, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> (rare use, but here <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on the observer’s experience) <b>see before (one) <a href='B:510 2:25'>Ac 2:25</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in temporal sense, <b>foresee <a href='B:510 2:31'>2:31</a>; <a href='B:550 3:8'>Gal 3:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> in combination of spatial and temporal sense, <b>see previously <a href='B:510 21:29'>Ac 21:29</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πρόοιδα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προορίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}